In January Drum magazine ran an article where it claimed Penny Penny had confirmed that he was Cassper's father."He calls me and we talk. He is very stubborn like me, but he knows I'm his father," the magazine quoted him as saying.Cassper's mother, Muzuki Phoolo, embarked on legal action against both the magazine and Penny Penny.Earlier this year Sowetan reported that Penny Penny escaped the legal action after he told Cassper's mom that he had been misquoted. The paper also reported that Muzuki had reached on an out of court settlement with Drum. Penny Penny was on DJ Sbu's breakfast radio show and took the opportunity to explain his side of the story.Watch the video here: video